org.cef.handler

Class CefLoadHandlerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.handler.CefLoadHandlerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CefLoadHandler 

    public abstract class CefLoadHandlerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements CefLoadHandler
    An abstract adapter class for receiving load events. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating handler objects.(用于接收加载事件的抽象适配器类。此类中的方法为空。此类的存在是为了方便创建处理程序对象。)

      • onLoadEnd

        public void onLoadEnd(CefBrowser browser,
                      CefFrame frame,
                      int httpStatusCode)
        Description copied from interface: CefLoadHandler
        Called when the browser is done loading a frame. The frameIdentifer value will never be empty. Multiple frames may be loading at the same time. Sub-frames may start or continue loading after the main frame load has ended. This method will always be called for all frames irrespective of whether the request completes successfully.(当浏览器加载完frame时调用。frameIdentifer值永远不会为空。多个frame可能同时加载。子frame可以在主frame加载结束后开始或继续加载。无论请求是否成功完成，都将始终为所有frame调用此方法。)
        Specified by:
        onLoadEnd in interface CefLoadHandler
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        frame - The frame generating the event. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(frame-生成事件的frame。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        httpStatusCode - The status code of the load.(httpStatusCode-加载的状态代码。)

        Description copied from interface: CefLoadHandler

      • onLoadingStateChange

        public void onLoadingStateChange(CefBrowser browser,
                                 boolean isLoading,
                                 boolean canGoBack,
                                 boolean canGoForward)
        Description copied from interface: CefLoadHandler
        Called when the loading state has changed. This callback will be executed twice -- once when loading is initiated either programmatically or by user action, and once when loading is terminated due to completion, cancellation of failure.(在加载状态更改时调用。此回调将执行两次：一次是在通过编程或用户操作启动加载时执行，另一次是由于加载完成而终止时执行，即取消失败。)
        Specified by:
        onLoadingStateChange in interface CefLoadHandler
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        isLoading - true if it is loading.(isLoading-如果正在加载，则为true。)
        canGoBack - true if you can navigate back.(canGoBack-如果您可以导航返回，则为true。)
        canGoForward - true if you can navigate forward.(canGoForward-如果您可以向前导航，则为true。)

      • onLoadStart

        public void onLoadStart(CefBrowser browser,
                        CefFrame frame,
                        CefRequest.TransitionType transitionType)
        Description copied from interface: CefLoadHandler
        Called when the browser begins loading a frame. The frameIdentifer value will never be empty. Multiple frames may be loading at the same time. Sub-frames may start or continue loading after the main frame load has ended. This method may not be called for a particular frame if the load request for that frame fails. For notification of overall browser load status use onLoadingStateChange instead.(当浏览器开始加载frame时调用。frameIdentifer值永远不会为空。多个frame可能同时加载。子frame可以在主frame加载结束后开始或继续加载。如果特定frame的加载请求失败，则可能不会对该frame调用此方法。有关浏览器整体加载状态的通知，请改用LoadingStateChange。)
        Specified by:
        onLoadStart in interface CefLoadHandler
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        frame - The frame generating the event. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(frame-生成事件的frame。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        transitionType - The transition type.(transitionType-转换类型。)
